name: Stylish Modern Bamboo Baby BIB ... Pink & Charcoal Flowers
description:
Made with super soft Bamboo velour and quality cotton fabric this stylish modern Baby Bib is designed to be that 'dribble catcher' you take on outings etc .... The bamboo fabric makes it super absorbent so baby will stay dry ... It makes a wonderful gift either on its own or as a supplement ... easily post-able!
Measuring about 33cm (13") tall & 20cm (8") wide
Handmade in Australia
Cold Hand or Gentle Machine wash
Line Dry or Dry Flat - Do Not Tumble Dry or Dry Clean

anti bacterial
soft & snuggly
environmental
biodegradable
ethical
pesticide free
absorbent
cool in summer
